    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>These gloves of thick leather do not impair delicate work and grant a +4 competence bonus on Disable Device checks to disable magic traps. Once per day, a wearer trained in Disable Device can command the gloves to alter an unattended magic item she touches to incorporate a trap. The wearer attempts a caster level check using the higher of her caster level or the gloves' caster level (DC = 11 + the target item's caster level). If the check is successful, the target item is marked with a glyph of warding (blast glyph only) that lasts for up to 1 day.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> </p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Wondrous Item, glyph of warding</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Inner Sea Intrigue",
